Define values for wall
Get image for wall
Set values for wall right, wall left, wall top and wall bottom
													

Define ball

ball top is equal to top ball value
ball bottom is equal to the bottom ball value
ball left is equal to left ball value 
ball right is equal to right ball value  
						


Define ball movement 
Wall Hit

If ball right is greater than wall left 
move ball left 
hit set to true
return hit


If ball bottom is greater than wall top
move ball up
hit set to true
return hit

If ball top is less than well bottom
move ball down
hit set to true
return hit

If ball left is less than wall right
move ball right
hit set to true
return hit
